          <p>Rule 13.70. Observance of schedule required; exception
Each standing committee shall hold regular meetings on the day, at the hour, and at the place designated for regular meetings during each week of the session. Â However, no committee shall be required to meet on any day assigned to it if there is no business to come before it or if prior notice of cancellation has been given.</p>
